Q1
How do we get rid of an object?

MyObject obj = new MyObject();
// Use the object
obj = null;  // Now the object is eligible for garbage collection

Q2
Create a small demo to understand variable scope in java

public class Main {
   public static void main(String[] args) {
     System.out.println(x);
     int X = 100;
   }
 }

Can't print X because we haven't made it yet since the sout is above X

Q3
What's the constructor called that has parameters

A constructor that has parameters are parametrized constructors

public Student(String name, int age) {
        this.name = name;
        this.age = age;
    }
